1. get a snapshot from http://xtables-addons.git.sourceforge.net
2. for snapshot: patch the source into its directory tree
3. comment all lines in mconfig
4. dependency: linux headers for your kernel, autoconf, automake, libtool
4. ./autogen.sh
5. ./configure --prefix=/usr ...
6. make
7. make install
8. iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --sport 80 -j ZHANG;
   iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 80 -j CUI
